<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to {{appName}}!</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        /* Base styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }

        /* Container styles */
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        /* Feature box */
        .feature-box {
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        /* Feature icon */
        .feature-icon {
            color: #3b82f6;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        /* Button styles */
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Responsive styles */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100% !important;
            }

            .button {
                width: 100% !important;
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    {{> header}}

    <div class="container">
        <h2 style="color: #1f2937; margin-top: 20px;">Welcome to {{appName}}!</h2>

        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>

        <p>Thank you for joining {{appName}}! We're excited to have you as part of our community. Your account has been
            successfully created and is ready to use.</p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            {{#trackButton loginUrl "Get Started" emailId "button"}}{{/trackButton}}
        </div>

        <h3 style="color: #1f2937; margin-top: 30px;">Key Features of {{appName}}</h3>

        <div class="feature-box">
            <p><span class="feature-icon">✓</span> <strong>Secure Communication</strong>: Our platform uses
                industry-leading encryption to keep your communications safe.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">
            <p><span class="feature-icon">✓</span> <strong>User-Friendly Interface</strong>: Our intuitive design makes
                sending and receiving emails a breeze.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">
            <p><span class="feature-icon">✓</span> <strong>Advanced Analytics</strong>: Track your email performance
                with detailed analytics and reports.</p>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is always here to
            help.</p>

        <p>We hope you enjoy using {{appName}}!</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>

    {{> footer recipient=to emailId=id}}
</body>

</html>